name: Rapid Deployment (V)
Lore: 'General Solo''s strike team was made up of the Alliance''s finest ground troops.',
Text: 'Target a site. At same and related sites, Rebel scouts deploying from hand are deploy -2 (and they may not battle or move) for remainder of turn. OR Deploy a Rebel scout (deploy +2) to a site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
